  "name": "Genetic loci associated with winter survivorship in diverse lowland switchgrass populations: SNP read count data",
  "author": {
    "name": "Hari Prasad Poudel",
    "givenName": "Hari Prasad",
    "familyName": "Poudel",
    "affiliation": {
